The interviewees talk about why they have decided to live in Tokyo, and what
it means to be black in Japan. The documentary is the first instalment of
[Melanin Unscripted](http://www.melaninunscripted.com/about/), the first in a
series of films by Nwosu aimed at â€œuncovering the complex identities that are
not generally projected in mainstream media.

